{"tid":2301272,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葡 國 混 血 巨 乳 女 星 歌 迪 蘿 直 播 被 禽 獸 包 圍 褻 玩 波 波","createTime":"2020-11-26T07:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T10:30:34.000Z","uid":97606,"like":1697,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"e6edcfa1e871f837c847f858e2abb623c4ea550b","tid":2301272,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201126/photo/bkn-20201126150555657-1126_00862_001_01p.jpg?20201126151755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201126150555657-1126_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20201126151755&h=92f69b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人肥媽（Maria Cordero）的丈夫Rick月頭因病離世，經過一段時間休息和沉澱後，肥媽終於走出喪夫陰霾，重新振作投入生活。她在社交網上載短片，見她與愛犬玩波波，隨手一掟狗狗便爭相追出拾回，十分乖巧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201126/photo/bkn-20201126150555657-1126_00862_001_02p.jpg?20201126151755\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201126%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201126150555657-1126_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20201126151755&h=cae8325d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肥媽似乎重拾歡容走出傷痛，她表示：「好耐都冇陪過狗狗玩波，今日同佢哋玩玩波，大家都走動吓。」她亦實踐丈夫臨終前許下的承諾，會繼續開Live教煮餸：「今個星期6如常開Live，至於煮咩同同步煮仲諗緊，稍後再話畀大家知。」"},{"pid":"b5aaaab7a957497d93829edc4bb8b320c96fa671","tid":2301272,"uid":354738,"like":1260,"dislike":4,"score":1256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:37:45.000Z","msg":"屌我認我咸濕"},{"pid":"4315c6ad8561b3012f4fc8fa3cccbb0d77ee50b0","tid":2301272,"uid":362766,"like":200,"dislike":0,"score":200,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T07:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認我咸濕"},{"pid":"5015cefa78d2bf0da6023e34022f966e92510032","tid":2301272,"uid":242737,"like":360,"dislike":1,"score":359,"citedBy":0,"re